@branley21 @nbatopshot Yea I guess that is the question do you want this to mirror physical cards or be an altogether different model, imo many people aren't interested in gambling money away on physical cards but prefer TS bc they feel more in control & able to carefully weigh the EV of each decision

@branley21 @nbatopshot +EV packs are fine so long as they are hard to get, hence the purpose of CS-gated drops

But my problem isn't so much the EV of the pack, it's the distribution of the EV across the pack, in these new packs 75% are -$10 EV, that is a large portion of the packs that are taking an L

The new @nbatopshot pack drop system is good for new collectors to now have the chance at a high tier moment right away... however I don't like paying an inflated pack price just for a miniscule chance at a legendary, feels more like a gamble & makes the median pack much more -EV
